// ==UserScript==
// @name TorrentDownloads

// @connect *://www.torrentdownloads.me/*
// @trackerURL http://www.torrentdownloads.me/search/
// @version 1.0
// @require exKit
// ==/UserScript==

var code = {
  "version": 2,
  "type": "kit",
  "uid": 545528478,
  "icon": "data:image/x-icon;base64,%3D",
  "title": "Torrent Downloads",
  "desc": "",
  "search": {
    "torrentSelector": {
      "title": "p>a",
      "url": {
        "selector": "p>a",
        "attr": "href"
      },
      "size": "span:eq(3)",
      "seed": "span:eq(2)",
      "peer": "span:eq(1)"
    },
    "onGetValue": {
      "size": [
        "convertSize"
      ]
    },
    "searchUrl": "http://www.torrentdownloads.me/search/?search=%search%",
    "baseUrl": "http://www.torrentdownloads.me/search/",
    "listItemSelector": "div.left_container>div.left_shadow:eq(1)>div>div>div>div>div>div>div.grey_bar3",
    "listItemSplice": [
      "1",
      0
    ]
  }
};

API_exKit(code);
